snippet.title: Johnny Depp faces career heartbreak after losing in court | Latinx Now! | Telemundo English
snippet.description:
Latinx Now! Johnny Depp, Amber Heard, and The Sun have finalized their court hearings, but according to Depp it is far from the over. See what the star said about his forced resignation and court results on Latinx Now!
